<li>Drive to <strong>Grizzly Paw Brewing</strong> in Canmore for a tour and tasting</li>
<li>Walk to <strong>Three Bears Brewery</strong> for afternoon pizza and beer</li>
<li>Return to Banff for evening drinks at <strong>The Rose & Crown</strong> rooftop</li>
</ol>
<p><em>Note: Designate a driver, take a taxi, or use Roam Transit between Banff and Canmore.</em></p>

<div class="tip-box"><strong>Beer & Stay:</strong> Find great accommodation near Banff's brewery district on <a href="https://www.expedia.ca/Hotel-Search?destination=Banff%2C+Alberta&camref=1101l3MtWX" target="_blank" rel="noopener sponsored">Expedia</a> — many downtown Banff hotels are a short walk from Banff Ave Brewing Co. and The Rose & Crown.</div>
